### Test Topic Stats API (Detailed Format)

### 1. Get Top Topics (Activity Score)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=activityScore
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Get Top Topics (Member Count)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=memberCount
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get Top Topics (Repos Count)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=reposCount
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get Top Topics (Code Analysis)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=codeAnalysis
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Topics with Stats by Course
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/COURSE_ID/course/stats?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=activityScore&order=DESC
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Topic Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/TOPIC_ID/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Expected Response Format:
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "topic-id",
      "title": "Topic Title",
      "memberCount": 5,
      "reposCount": 3,
      "commit": {
